1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,840
Can you read this out loud for me? "Big brother."

2
00:00:02,240 --> 00:00:03,480
That's disgusting.

3
00:00:04,560 --> 00:00:05,640
You're the younger brother.

4
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:08,920
What's gotten into you?

5
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:10,280
You were the one who said we should keep our distance.

6
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:11,280
Actually, that was you.

7
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:16,160
What is your deal?

8
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:17,640
In your collection,

9
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:19,720
there seem to be quite a few stories about brothers.

10
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:21,200
Give that back!

11
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:26,440
That's not it...

12
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,720
Deep down, you've always wanted a big brother, haven't you?

13
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,240
No, I haven't.

14
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:33,320
Even if that were true,

15
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:35,400
I've never accepted you as my brother.

16
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:40,000
Hey, don't talk to Kono Mizuki like that!

17
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:40,760
No, but that guy...!

18
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:42,400
We're brothers, blood or not.

19
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:44,000
Try to get along.

20
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:47,080
Alright, let's dig in.

21
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:48,680
Dig in!

22
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:49,680
- Dig in.
- This looks delicious.

23
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,920
I'm going on a trip with Satoru-san tomorrow.

24
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:54,080
Sorry about that.

25
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:56,320
We're heading off for a hot spring getaway, just the two of us.

26
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,080
Huh?

27
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,680
You're going to be out tomorrow?

28
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,400
That's right.

29
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:04,440
In that case...

30
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:05,600
It'll just be the two of us tomorrow.

31
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,240
What are we going to do about dinner?

32
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:11,240
I'll leave you some money.

33
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,720
You've got to be kidding me.

34
00:01:13,720 --> 00:01:15,200
I have to be stuck alone with this guy?

35
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,120
I have a bad feeling about this.
